<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Born into an academic family - his father is a history lecturer at Winchester University College (formerly King Alfred's College) in Winchester and his mother is a comparative religions lecturer at the Open University - Colin Firth's first acting experience came in infant's school when he played "Jack Frost" in a Christmas pantomime. Three of his ...            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0000147/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm" >See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
